==Pro Tools loop record enable==


To loop record enable [[Pro Tools]] you can either right click on the record enable button and choose '''Loop''' or go to '''Options>Loop Record'''

When you are done the record button will have a Loop circle displayed within it. 


[[File:Pro Tools Record button with loop record enabled.png]]


This can be used to [[Pro Tools:Recording multiple takes|create multiple takes]] within Pro Tools 

